{"tid":2114612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最近幾日，(國安法)變左高官敏感詞……","createTime":"2020-07-19T03:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T09:01:45.000Z","uid":268286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0de0a203c8dd57d3945ee4d9305939fe4aca7e5d","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:37:08.000Z","msg":"上星期初選之後班官就咩都話：懷疑觸犯國安法！<br />\n<br />\n搞到Ｄ人連飲水都要問下自己有冇犯到國安法。<br />\n<br />\n好神奇，尼二日竟然無官提(國安法)三個字，唔知係咪失左憶！<br />\n<br />\n基於愛國原因，市民記者議員要做好責任，多Ｄ於公眾場合提問高官，市有冇犯國安法。甘，邊個支持(國安法)就可以記錄在案，從而得到佢地應得既( 獎勵)！"},{"pid":"8cb4014ce0e10dfe01632a9abad9ca11d939edd6","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:41:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"098845e1f3aa54c0759a1cb05e3cc9a43936b4f6","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b157741113fb554181d10ce733065a36b094ef76","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"097bf6b1bc5b7a98d262b06a75c0920bb2bc51eb","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:43:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c8a5991e5aad4220ab49b5b9d331a2f32e0eaa8e","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"469873809b9f15c5b7255e400d280fa8dcd0e0e8","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4ae9629c8e127ce1f8b33af53640d2a0ca80d40f","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1698cae61cc4d106b6062082264cae537bf495fe","tid":2114612,"uid":268286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}